CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 16, 1946, pg. 18, reads: "Cage Team - Members of the Alpha Phi Alpha basketball team, who will play the Centre Avenue Y Big Five Friday, Feb. 15, at 9 P.M. Members, left to right, back row, are Sgt. Bart Wallace, Morris Fountain, Lieut. Benny Taylor, Sgt. Orville Bates, Lieut. Jesse Gloster. Kneeling: Frank Craft and William Norvall.  Not Shown in picture are Max Thompson, LuGene Bray and Toulton McCollough.  In the preliminary, the Y Vikings will play the Y Vets, composed of such players as Beatsid Pollard, Champ Lewis, Pat Royster, Ernie Myers and Bill Ford. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Alpha Phi Alpha basketball players, standing from left: Bart Wallace, Morris Fountain, Bennie Taylor, Orville Bates, Jesse Gloster; kneeling: Frank Craft and William Norvall, posed in Centre Avenue YMCA
